================================================================================
  QUICK START
================================================================================

1. Navigate to project:
   cd C:\Users\n0l08i7\Documents\supplier-search-engine

2. View statistics:
   python cli.py stats

3. Search suppliers:
   python cli.py search --query "Electronics"

4. List products:
   python cli.py list-products --supplier-id 1

5. Add new supplier:
   python cli.py add-supplier --supplier-id "NEWSUP001" --name "New Corp" --category "Electronics"

